{"tid":903009,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"鯽魚涌的午餐日記 15","createTime":"2018-11-15T08:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T11:58:30.000Z","uid":28951,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d761d536da2e764cba00cdbca7a9c8da98f59eb5","tid":903009,"uid":28951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:41:52.000Z","msg":"由於琴日食咗個好伏嘅吉列豬，今日都冇乜心情食飯。<br />\n<br />\n所以簡食西嘢，係冇嘢嘅時候去CAFE坐下都係唔錯嘅選擇。<br />\n<br />\n呢間餐廳係門面比較細，位置都比較偏。<br />\n<br />\n大約二十個位左右，一個侍應一個大廚，冇乜特別裝修，簡簡單單。<br />\n<br />\n同時亦都冇乜客坐係度，一個幾寧靜嘅空間。<br />\n<br />\n餐牌都冇乜特色食品，都係意粉同All day呢啲大路嘢。<br />\n<br />\n落單：番茄雞肉扁意粉+熱朱古力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先上左個熱朱古力，雖然拉花好似有啲歪但完全可以接受。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L7UrnuK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL7UrnuK.png&h=3a1e9ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n味道唔會太甜，朱古力味亦唔係好濃烈，我個人比較鐘意種呢種程度，唔會好似7仔個啲咁驚死你唔知係乜飲緊乜。<br />\n<br />\n所有餐都係即叫即煮，但由於人唔多，又唔需要特別煮法，所以都好快上枱。<br />\n<br />\n賣相雖然有啲亂，但都唔差。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jUZrnuR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjUZrnuR.png&h=707772ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n番茄食唔出罐頭味，唔酸，唔濃郁但亦非淡而無味。<br />\n<br />\n面頭個幾片芝士用於裝飾多於提升味道。<br />\n<br />\n雞肉撳落質感比較結實，入口首先係煎過嘅焦香，調味適中唔太鹹，雖然質感比較硬但食落中間並唔粗嚡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結：環境舒服，好寧靜，Hea下或者同朋友吹下水都唔錯。味道偏淡，選擇少咗啲，整體不俗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfac3d8801e6d3728eff296969686bcc15e1374e","tid":903009,"uid":140941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:42:58.000Z","msg":"同路人<br />\n日日一個係鰂魚涌食"},{"pid":"213109d1b4a9256601563bf3bd4e04d17bd075e5","tid":903009,"uid":177719,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6700c1aab1d31088e0623378bd0b207b546eb96","tid":903009,"uid":147710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"213109d1b4a9256601563bf3bd4e04d17bd075e5","tid":903009,"uid":177719,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"樓主連和富都計"},{"pid":"91058a83969304f2b80d18542aaeabb8c398fd23","tid":903009,"uid":177719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6700c1aab1d31088e0623378bd0b207b546eb96","tid":903009,"uid":147710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"213109d1b4a9256601563bf3bd4e04d17bd075e5","tid":903009,"uid":177719,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"樓主連和富都計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T11:58:30.000Z","msg":"當炮台山都仲叫有道理<br />\n點會計qb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}